data.title: Lanton
data.description: Thick glass trophy with exclusive design and resistant base. Specially designed for laser engraving and presented in a protective case made of durable cardboard, with magnetic closure and foam, die-cut interior.

similar.title: Lanrok
similar.description: Lunchbox Limited Edition. A fascinating design that combines design, functionality and sustainability. Composed of a main compartment in stainless steel of 1 litre capacity, hermetic lid in bamboo and base in natural cork. Includes safety strap.  From the perfect combination of exclusivity and design, come Limited Edition, a special collection of limited edition promotional ideas. A new concept, inspired by the fusion of premium products with the latest and most innovative trends and with a limited selection available, turn a gift into a unique and unforgettable experience.  Exclusive Limited Edition presentation case, with a design protected by industrial property rights.  Including card with description of Limited Edition in recycled cardboard.

similar.title: Halderan
similar.description: Elegant premium set, including:Double-walled thermos cup in stainless steel. 640 ml capacity, with bamboo area on the lid for branding. Soft PU notepad with integrated smartphone holder on the cover and bamboo area for branding. Including elastic closure, bookmark and matching color pen holder. Presented in an individual, matte-finish case with magnetic closure, including inner die-cutting for each of the sets elements.
